questions: What is the resolution for the error "The GUI version 0.8.0 does not match the API version"?
How to ensure that the docker version of GUI and API is the same?
What is the process to check the versions of GUI and API?
answer:
# Error The GUI version 0.8.0 does not match the API version

This indicates that the API version and GUI version is not the same. Click on Tracardi name in the menu to see the versions. 
TO resolve this issue make sure that the docker version of GUI and API is the same.
